1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/sujanrajtuladhar/screen-pet.git
   ```

2. Navigate to the project directory:
   ```bash
   cd screen-pet
   ```

3. Install the dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

4. Start the application:
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

5. Open your browser and go to `http://localhost:3000` to view the application., branch: add-setup-docs